rComments: Prof C's property course was great. Her slideshows are in-depth, she is great at explaining complicated issues, and she has great energy when teaching. She doesn't assign frivolous readings, they're almost all directly relevant to what will be expected of you on the exam (and she will tell you about any that aren't). Highly recommend!
Prof C is amazing! She is super friendly and happy to answer any questions you might have, and her lectures are great. 10/10 definitely recommend!
